modName: Chaos star bikini UNP CBBE UNPB BBP - DELETED
summary: skimpy light armor, craftable  in leather. Top, belt, trousers. Few color variants. UNP, UNPB BBP, CBBE for now.
descriptionHtml:
Armor is light armor, craftable in leather, temperable, supports weight slider, base armor is 36  for each piece.
Has 3 pieces: top, belt, trousers
Name begins from "chaos"
Made for UNP (latest) body, converted for CBBE 3.4f (latest) and UNPB BBP 2.52 (latest)

Top (slot 32) and belt (slot 56): ebony, copper, gold, steel
Trousers (slot 32): copperblack, coppergreen, ebonywhite, goldred, goldpurp, goldblue, steelblack, steelred

If you want version with shoes gloves necklace you can download it [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/87367]here[/url]

F.A.Q.
Q: Do you plan to make it for other bodytypes/change armor type/add other pieces?
A: Perhaps, if mod will be popular.

Q: Can I make retexture/conversion to other body and upload it on nexus?
A: You are welcome. Just remember to give me credits and link to original mod.

-------------------Changelog-----------------------------
v1.01 Little changed colored textures on trousers - made them more bright.
Well if you have previous version installed - not sure if you will notice difference.

-------------------Permissions---------------------------
You can do whatever you want while it is non-commercial destribution and you give me credits
and thanks as original author.
I don't give permission to upload it to steam.
